<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ910405-0079</DOCNO><DOCID>910405-0079.</DOCID><HL>   Precision Castparts Acquisition</HL><DATE>04/05/91</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION</SO><CO>   PCP</CO><MS>TECHNOLOGY (TEC)</MS><IN>AEROSPACE (ARO)TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)</IN><RE>OREGON (ORG)</RE><LP>   PORTLAND, Ore. -- Precision Castparts Corp. said it agreedto purchase Advanced Forming Technology Inc., a closely heldmaterials maker in Longmont, Colo., for about $13 million.   Precision Castparts, a maker of specialized materials,said it expects the transaction to close next month.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>